  notes: 'Level adi: Level_24

    Boyut: 33x18

    Zorluk: Tum mekanikler 2

    Mekanik
    ozeti: Daha uzun renk sirasi: Blue lock, Red plate bridge, Purple toggle, Yellow
    door ve final jump. Donus looplari eklendi.

    Start koordinati: (1,2)

    Goal
    koordinati: (31,16)

    Renkli kilitler: YellowButton (8,5) link=B24 face=Purple;
    YellowDoor (4,7) link=B24 face=Purple; YellowButton (23,11) link=Y24 face=White;
    YellowDoor (29,9) link=Y24 face=White

    PressurePlate requiredFace bilgisi:
    (23,8) requiredFace=Yellow, mode=Toggle, singleUse=False; (10,7) requiredFace=Purple,
    mode=ActivateOnly, singleUse=False

    ToggleBridge bilgisi: (17,6) link=R24,
    startsActive=False; (26,4) link=P24, startsActive=False

    OneTimeTile koordinatlari:
    (27,4) h0; (28,4) h0

    IceSlide rotalari: IceDownStart(18,6) -> IceMiddle(19,6)
    -> IceMiddle(20,6) -> IceLanding(21,6)

    GreenJump ve JumpLanding koordinatlari:
    Jump (29,12) h0; Landing (31,12) h0

    RedBreakable koordinatlari: (12,13)
    h0

    Gelistirici test cozum rotasi: Right, Right, Right, Right, Right, Right,
    Right, Up, Up, Up, Up, Up, Right, Right, Right, Up, Up, Up, Up, Up, Up, Down,
    Down, Down, Down, Down, Down, Down, Down, Down, Down, Down, Down, Down, Right,
    Right, Right, Right, Right, Right, Up, Up, Up, Up, Up, Down, Down, Down, Down,
